title: Star Wars Episode 3 - Backstroke of the West (HiDt)
description:
Star War: The Third Gathers: Backstroke of the West  is the hilarious recursive translation of  Star Wars: Episode 3: Revenge of the Sith.

It was first discovered by Jeremy Winterson ( <a href=" http://winterson.com/2009/01/episode-iii-backstroke-of-west-redux.html" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://winterson.com/2009/01/episode-iii-backstroke-of-west-redux.html</a>  )

In 2010, it was dubbed by a group known as TheThirdGathers (  ) and uploaded in segments to YouTube and Vimeo.

Those segments are available here: <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7270205" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7270205</a>

This is a complete copy, muxed into HiDt's 720p release of RotS.


Features:
720p video (h.264)

5.1 DTS audio (original English)
2 commentary tracks
Backstroke of the West (dubbed audio)

Subtitles:
Original English
Russian
Chinese
Greek
Portugese
Spanish
Backstroke of the West subtitles

Enjoy!
